classitems.description:
Registered keys.

    {
        "key": [ "id", "id", ... ]
        ...
    }

Keyboard bindings.

    {
        "id": {
            safe: Boolean,
            callback: Function,
            binding: Object
        },
        ...
    }

Icons.

    {
         "iconName": [x, y],
         "icon2": [x2, y2],
         ...
    }

Register a callback for any PhotonUI/Widget event (called wEvent).

Callback signature:

    function (Object(Base/Widget) [, arg1 [, arg2 [, ...]]])
